name: Purple Dino Necklace:)
description:
<big>This adorable Dino Necklace is the best (and cutest) thing since sliced bread and mixtapes!

Like everything else in this store, it is especially handmade just for YOU! The Dinosaur itself is purple and the spots on it are a periwinkle shade. I handcraft the Dinosaurs so not everyone will be identical, which will add even more of a unique quality to your purchase! 

It's bound to be the highlight of your wardrobe:)

And it's shipped directly to you in super snazzy packaging!
</big>

name: Mini Retro Rubix Cube Necklace
description:
<big>This colourful necklace features the one and only Rubix Cube!
It's is sure to bring lots of razz-ma-tazz to your outfit:)

The necklace brings old school memories back to life, with 3 neon coloured necklaces! 

The six sides of this magical cube are coloured red, orange, yellow, green, blue..and pink! The cube itself measeures 3x3x3 cm(1.2"x1.2")-and guess what-it's solvable too! It comes attatched to a lanyard necklace, measuring 61 cm (24").

If you need a longer or shorter neck length, just contact me and I'll be happy to help you!
</big>
